      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Johan$<BR>My kind are usually hostile towards humans.<BR>
...Honestly, I also don't think that all the humans are good.<BR>
But us, or the humans, or the elves, we are all children of the Goddess.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n714_cleric_yohan-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n714_cleric_yohan-accepting-b" mid="18" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>But natives and humans wouldn't be able to reconcile</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n714_cleric_yohan-accepting-c" mid="19" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>You're too naïve</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n714_cleric_yohan-accepting-d" mid="20" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>All the types of people are allies against the Dragon Followers</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n714_cleric_yohan-accepting-e" mid="21" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>There are good people among the natives too</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Johan$<BR>I believe that the humans, us, and the elves.... We all have the light that Goddess gave us inside us.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n714_cleric_yohan-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Johan$<BR>
Do you think so?<BR>
Hmm, I know for sure that the conflict between the two will not be solved overnight.<BR>
But I hope one day the we can live peacefully together.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n714_cleric_yohan-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Johan$<BR>
I only believe and follow the truth.<BR>
I don't know if that's something that I should be teased about.<BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Johan looks at you like he's hurt)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n714_cleric_yohan-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Johan$<BR>
That's right. We have to fight together until the evil Dragon Follower are gone!!<BR>
Fighting among ourselves only helps that treacherous group.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n714_cleric_yohan-accepting-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Johan$<BR>
<FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, if there are more people like you, there will be a day when the two will understand each other.</html>]]></talk_question>
